果啲<br />\n而家只不過係可以將平時調酒嘅野直接倒喺地下先<br />\n白磷、鋁粉都ok，幾易準備<br />\n再加糖、花生醬<br />\n<br />\nBtw TNT係chem人嘅知識，chem major大學生都會知道點合成，唔可能有現成俾人買，當然合成出黎要好小心，唔好炸親自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"重點係要準確引爆先至要玩remote detonator"},{"pid":"61b9648d28b03777409bdd498818d572dfae819e","tid":1615250,"uid":50880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"戰術po冇人睇"},{"pid":"5bde8bdecc2d4361cccdd367277279fa6f2a3f26","tid":1615250,"uid":50880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"其實我地好需要後勤部準備物資攞上黎用<br />\n你唔敢上頭排都幫下手整野丫<br />\n好多人都仲要返工返學，閒時要搬運物資收藏物資安排藏身點都已經好撚煩，而家仲要玩埋反跟蹤<br />\n好需要後勤部幫手DIY"},{"pid":"7092a1f807a9db2631c020a7bfa25a27814b018b","tid":1615250,"uid":50880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"屌那星心都灰鳩埋"},{"pid":"c0aa0191716f551be1aceca74ea81cb62a209955","tid":1615250,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:56:11.000Z","msg":"Goyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd34db1468884c65d6ce7939e6ab5822c17c2e83","tid":1615250,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q1aHbRlcing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ1aHbRlcing&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=9a102e3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q1aHbRlcing</a> 獵魔士"},{"pid":"b64fe06566edc589244df1505372b5adeba492da","tid":1615250,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:01:49.000Z","msg":"銀髮軍師 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非加入 戰況大增千倍</span>的新戰術<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613583</a>"}]}